    "ChatGPT launched in November 2022.",
    "By July 2025, 18 billion messages were being sent each week by 700 million users, representing around 10% of the global adult population.",
    "1 For a new technology, this speed of global diffusion has no precedent (Bick et al., 2024).",
    "This paper studies consumer usage of ChatGPT, the first mass-market chatbot and likely the largest.",
    "2 ChatGPT is based on a Large Language Model (LLM), a type of Artificial Intelligence (AI) developed over the last decade and generally considered to represent an acceleration in AI capabilities."
